GSD.product_version: versions from v4.12 to before v6.1.9
GSD.description:
bnxt: Do not read past the end of test names

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.1.9 by commit cefa85480ac99c0bef5a09daadb48d65fc28e279, it was introduced in version v4.12 by commit eb51365846bc418687af4c4f41b68b6e84cdd449. For more details please see the references link.
